Mining Feature Service
======================

Maven
=====

The service is built using maven so a prerequisite to building is to have maven installed on your machine.
Maven installation instructions can be found here: http://maven.apache.org/install.html

Build
=====
 
1. Unzip the mining-feature-service.zip file to a preferred folder
2. From the command line run following maven command in the same folder
   mvn clean package  

This will create the jar file in the target folder

Run
===

1. From the command line, go to the target folder that contains the jar file using the following command
   cd ./target
2. Issue the following command to run the service
   java -jar MiningFeatureService-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
   
The mines found within the required boundary will be listed 




